    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/e75b9fd6b9cf84900340f0226b7e7123.avif?t=1746169242\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一连串诡异神秘的谋杀案将 Eddy —— 一位身无分文、落魄的记者 —— 引向一座看似偏远的豪宅后，他很快意识到自己并不孤单。Eddy 必须在这座宅邸中穿行、解开谜题，逐步接近真相……同时努力生存，躲避那未知的“存在”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索：</strong> 探索周围环境，收集线索，解决谜题，帮助 Eddy 更接近真相的揭示。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/92cfc6a5cdcaf6e5f2f977b2e0cd0c87.poster.avif?t=1746169242\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/92cfc6a5cdcaf6e5f2f977b2e0cd0c87.webm?t=1746169242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/92cfc6a5cdcaf6e5f2f977b2e0cd0c87.mp4?t=1746169242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭示：谋杀案并不是 Eddy 生命中的唯一谜题。随着在宅邸中停留的时间延长，他被迫直面自己过往的黑暗与问题</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/4b8cf0065b5ae6a63280c48527a6bd6a.poster.avif?t=1746169242\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/4b8cf0065b5ae6a63280c48527a6bd6a.webm?t=1746169242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/4b8cf0065b5ae6a63280c48527a6bd6a.mp4?t=1746169242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存： 探索周围环境时务必小心，总有一种感觉你并不孤单。利用周围有限的资源，帮助自己在豪宅中生存下来。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/5ae8be8e582311ebcfa2f9c2e5a3a608.poster.avif?t=1746169242\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/5ae8be8e582311ebcfa2f9c2e5a3a608.webm?t=1746169242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100420/extras/5ae8be8e582311ebcfa2f9c2e5a3a608.mp4?t=1746169242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
